  m_Name: Line_S6_End_HC_02
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Bonbibi.DialogueLine
  speaker: 0
  text: He told his mother that the forest provided. He didn't tell her everything.
    But the next morning, before anyone else was awake, he went back to Bonbibi's
    shrine and left something of his own. He didn't explain why. He didn't have the
    words for it yet. Maybe he would, someday.
